    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class</p><p>Prerequisite: Medical-Nin, Level 4+</p><p> </p><p>You learn from your peers how to manage your chakra, allowing you to better utilize your healing potential, allowing you to become more flexible in your restorative techniques. </p><p>You gain the following benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Your Rejuvenating Rest class feature, healing die is increased to d10's. </p><p>• Jutsu with the Medical Keyword that would benefit from your Channeled Healing class feature heals additional hit points equal to your Ninjutsu ability modifier, if it doesn't already.</p>",
